snippet.title: Bianca Tarot
snippet.description:
Welcome to my Channel !

I identify as a Psychic Tarot Reader, Light Worker & Healer here to share my gift with reading energy through tarot with the world ! On this channel, I offer celebrity tarot readings, monthly zodiac readings, missing persons/ unsolved cases readings , and free personalized pick a card readings for words of wisdom from spirit ! All of my readings come from pure intentions only ! For those who wish to book a reading or have any questions, please feel free to email me !

MY CELEBRITY READINGS ARE FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES ONLY.

Peace & Blessings
